  "features": [
    "Professional color schemes optimized for long coding sessions",
    "Four carefully crafted theme variants: Arctic, Midnight, Modern and Light",
    "High contrast ratios for enhanced readability and reduced eye strain",
    "Consistent syntax highlighting across 15+ programming languages",
    "Clean and modern workbench UI design",
    "Refined terminal and debug console experience",
    "Thoughtful semantic token coloring",
    "Harmonious bracket pair colorization",
    "Distinctive Git decoration colors",
    "Polished editor widget styling"
